    public class JoglPaneB
extends JoglPane
implements java.awt.event.KeyListener, java.awt.event.MouseListener, java.awt.event.MouseMotionListener, java.awt.event.ActionListener
    Represents a panel for drawing. The bulk of the graphics is done here. Extension of JoglPane for world building.
    Author:
    William Meng
